  "ai_usage": "Use for blog posts, docs prose, and articles. Copy the document and replace the title, byline, cover, and body. The key is the --measure (keep 60–75ch) and line-height for readability — don't widen the column. Headings, blockquote, and inline code are pre-styled. Pair with the scroll-progress-bar effect for a reading indicator. Set a real <time datetime>.",
